query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 s t1 tq1 q1) NoMergeJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('annotations',
'data-visualization',
'devexpress',
'foreach',
'interface',
'lua',
'radio-button',
'twitter-bootstrap',
'websphere') AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.score >= 1 AND q1.score <= 10
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100 group by t1.name;
